{"tid":1043253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]特朗普下令 中國要即時取消美國農產品關稅","createTime":"2019-03-02T06:21:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T10:42:37.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"737c5494518a533cc0ac0e415a9e0af11305b866","tid":1043253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普表示，已經要求中國立即取消向美國農產品徵收的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普在社交網站發文稱，美中貿易談判進展良好，已要求中國即時取消所有對美國農產品，包括牛肉和豬肉等的關稅。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普稱，他無按原計劃於3月1日調升中國貨品的關稅稅率至25%，這對美國偉大的農民和他自己來說都非常重要。"},{"pid":"04cca835496d9b05e44345a18826199bb78f83f4","tid":1043253,"uid":177089,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:27:01.000Z","msg":"下令？"},{"pid":"59de2d85528a320c4e10daaf7ee254873383c533","tid":1043253,"uid":28800,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e3e0596d1f614927b5f450ec7c63f5d0f60ddb9a","tid":1043253,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"59de2d85528a320c4e10daaf7ee254873383c533","tid":1043253,"uid":28800,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搵野挑佢機啫"},{"pid":"8d6d9cca66bec8bf33cb83c63f9b0ab361dc31fe","tid":1043253,"uid":35580,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59de2d85528a320c4e10daaf7ee254873383c533","tid":1043253,"uid":28800,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"molamola美帝要輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08688e598918cd886de34b0a5c6eee1cd39c6656","tid":1043253,"uid":121146,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T06:55:30.000Z","msg":"美國就快輸到破產喇  中國2025一定嬴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p